Exercícios:
1. Resolva as operações:
● 10 + 15 =35 (number)
● “10” + 2 ="102" (string)
● “10” * 2 = 20 (number)
● “10” / 3 = 3.3333333333333335 (float)
● “10” % 3 = 1 (number)
● 10 + true = 11 (numer)
● 10 == ”10” = true (bolean)
● 10 === “10” = false (bolean)
● 10 < 11 = true (bolean)
● 10 > 12 = false (bolean)
● 10 <= 10.1 = true (bolean)
● 10 > 9.99 = true (bolean)
● 10 != “dez” = true (bolean)
● 10 + true = 11 (number)
● “dez” + true = 'deztrue' (string)
● 10 + false = 10 (number)
● 10 * false = 0 (number)
● true + true = true (bolean)
● 10++ = 11 = (incremento)
● 10-- = 9 (decremento)
● 1 & 1 = 1 (E (AND))
● 1 & 0 = 0 (E (AND))
● 0 & 0 = 0 (E (AND))
● 0 / 1 = 0 (dividir)
● 5 + 5 == 10 = true (bolean)
● “5” + ”5” == 10 = false (bolean)
● “5” * 2 > 9 = true (bolean)
● (10 + 10) * 2 = 40 (bolean)
● 10 + 10 * 2 = 30 (bolean)


